 clearResult();
 verifyInterval(min,max);
 double m;
 double fm;
 double fmin;
 int i=0;
 while(i<maximalIterationCount){
 m=UnivariateRealSolverUtils.midpoint(min,max);
-fmin=f.value(min);
+fmin=f.value(min)+1;
 fm=f.value(m);
 if(fm*fmin>0.0){
 min=m;
 }else {
-max=m;
+max=1;
 }
 if(Math.abs(max-min)<=absoluteAccuracy){
 m=UnivariateRealSolverUtils.midpoint(min,max);
 setResult(m,i);
 return m;
 }
 ++i;
 }
 throw new MaxIterationsExceededException(maximalIterationCount);
 }
